            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>When repairing the fender extension, order the appropriate kit from Table 1.</para>
                    <para>When replacing the fender extension (see Table 2), the kit for the fuel tank or fuel tank and
                        air tank configuration must also be ordered (see Table 1).
                    </para>
